<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT92">
<l>eṉṟu maṟantaṟiyē ṉeṉṉeñcat tēvaittu</l>
<l>niṉṟu miruntum neṭumālai yeṉṟun</l>
<l>tiruvirunta mārpaṉ cirītaraṉuk kāḷāy</l>
<l>karuvirunta nāḷmutalāk kāppu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[Being] protected since the day [I] was in the womb,</l>
<l>I never forget [Him, whether] standing [or] sitting,</l>
<l>placing the tall Māl in my heart,</l>
<l>and becoming the slave of Śrīdhara, Him on whose chest Śrī sat forever.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
